%% Provisioning & onboarding sequence
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant UI as Dashboard
  participant API as Control API
  participant BILL as Stripe
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant PROV as Provisioner
  participant CLOUD as Cloud Provider
  participant NODE as VPN Node
  participant KS as KeyStore

  U->>UI: Purchase subscription
  UI->>API: Create subscription request
  API->>BILL: Create customer & subscription
  BILL-->>API: webhook subscription active
  API->>DB: persist subscription
  API->>KS: generate keys (WireGuard)
  API->>PROV: request node provisioning (region)
  PROV->>CLOUD: create VM / instance
  CLOUD-->>PROV: provisioned
  PROV->>NODE: bootstrap config + keys
  NODE-->>API: register node (health/metadata)
  API-->>U: return WireGuard config + QR
  U->>NODE: establish tunnel (connect)
  NODE->>API: usage session event
  API->>DB: record usage
